for your English assessment","english_test_result_not_found":"English assessment result not found","result":"Result","your_english_level_is":"Your English level is:","english_level_description":"According to a research carried out in 2004, 75% of Brazilian companies consider English language skills very useful on a daily basis and 37% of Brazilian companies claimed that the use of English has increased \\"very significantly\\" in the last three years. We want to help you understand your performance!","characteristics_of_your_profile":"Your profile characteristics","advanced_english":"English","english":"English","logic_test_result":"Logical reasoning result","check_the_result_of_your_logic_test":"Check out the results for your Logical Reasoning assessment","logic_test_result_not_found":"Logical reasoning result not found","your_logical_level_is":"Your logical reasoning level is:","logic_level_description":"Logical reasoning is one of the most valued skills in society, since it helps in our daily problem solving, especially in our work environment. Because of that, we want to help you understand your performance!","logical_result":"Logical reasoning","quantitative_result":"Quantitative thinking","step_register_reproved_description_03_plus":"Eliminatories questions:","step_register_reproved_description_03":"Eliminatory question:","other_vacancies_in_company":"Search for new vacancies at {companyName}","step_register_reproved_description_04":"Your resume is saved in our talent pool and can be used for future vacancies. Additionally, you can search for new opportunities on our career page.","step_register_reproved_description_01":"{companyName} has an update for your application in {jobName}","step_register_reproved_description_02":": Some of the questions were defined as elimination criteria, and unfortunately, your answer was not compatible with the established criteria. <strong>Therefore, it is not possible to continue in the selection process for this vacancy.</strong>","step_register_reproved_talent":"Your resume will remain saved in our talent pool. You can also search for new opportunities on the <a href=https://portal.gupy.io/ rel=noopener noreferrer target=_blank><strong>Gupy Job Portal</strong></a>.","how_you_will_send_the_video":"How will you send the video?","do_the_upload_on_youtube":"Upload the video on YouTube with the following title:","youtube_video_name_usage_sample":"GUPY_\\"YOUR_FIRST_NAME\\"_\\"YOUR_MIDDLE_NAME\\"_\\"MONTH\\"_\\"YEAR\\"","youtube_video_name_sample":"Example: GUPY_JOS\xC9_SILVA_11_2017","in_this_link_you_can_find_the_instructions_to_upload":"Here you will find instructions to upload your video on YouTube.","is_very_simple_click_at_following_link":"It's very easy! Check this link:","instructions_to_send_video":"Instructions to send the video","important_select_not_listed_option":"Important! Choose the privacy option \\"Not listed\\", so that your video will not be viewed by others.","now_you_know_how_to_do":"Now that you already know how to do it, copy and paste the link of your YouTube video","link_of_video":"Video link","fill_this_field_must_be_youtube_url":"Fill in this field. It is required that you use a YouTube URL","save":"Save","curriculum_skills_submit":"Save","save_last_block":"Save","/curriculum/components/footer/save":"Save","step_register_reproved_opportunities_button":"Search for new opportunities","step_register_reproved_vacancies_button":"Show My Applications","step_register_reproved_image_description":"Disapproval Icon","you_can_find_new_opportunities":"You can find a new opportunity on the Gupy job portal.","button_modal_timeline":"Got it!","activities_description_ok":"Got it!","helper_time_ago_minutes":"{count, plural, one {# minute} other {# minutes}}","helper_time_ago_hours":"{count, plural, one {# hour} other {# hours}}","helper_time_ago_days":"{count, plural, one {# day} other {# days}}","helper_time_ago_months":"{count, plural, one {# month} other {# months}}","helper_time_ago_years":"{count, plural, one {# year} other {# years}}","error_404_title":"We can\u2019t find the page you\u2019re looking for","error_404_title_description":"It\u2019s no longer possible to access this page. How about exploring other opportunities on our Job Board?","error_404_title_btn":"I want to see other opportunities","application-dashboard-title-description":"Follow below the progress of each step. If you would like to see the job description, <a href=\\"/jobs/{jobid}?jobBoardSource=gupy_opportunities\\" target=\\"_blank\\">click here</a>.","your_application_header":"About the process","your_progress":"Your progress","talent_pool_hint_description":"<strong>Talent Pool</strong><br/>Applying to the talent pool is a way to demonstrate your interest in future opportunities at the company. <a href=\u201Chttps://suporte-candidatos.gupy.io/s/suporte?language=pt_BR\u201D target=\\"_blank\\">Learn more</a>","about-company-header":"About us","application-tip-4":"The last move of people applying for this job happened <b>{jobLastMovementAtTimeAgo}</b> ago. Vacancy has been open for <b>{jobPushishedAtTimeAgo}</b>.","application-tip-5":"There has been no applicant activity for this vacancy. It has remained open for {jobPushishedAtTimeAgo}.","application-tip-2":"<b>Gupy\u2019s tip:</b> While you await the next steps, how about checking out some tips on how to prepare for an interview? <b><a href=\\"https://www.gupy.io/blog/entrevista-de-emprego\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noopener noreferrer\\">Learn more.</a></b>","application-tip-3":"Describing your professional experiences in detail can improve your chances of being noticed.","candidate-feedback-modal-company-will-analyze-your-data":"Step Finished!","candidate-feedback-modal-finished-step-from-company":"Now we\u2019ll analyze your compatibility with the job here at {companyName}, and we\u2019ll decide if you move on to the next steps.","candidate-feedback-modal-keep-attention-on-phone-and-email":"Keep an eye on your <b>e-mail</b> (including the spam box) and on the <b>phone number</b> you registered at our platform to find out about the next steps.<a href=https://login.gupy.io/candidates/profile target=_blank rel=noopener noreferrer ><b>How about checking if your information is up to date?</b></a>","position-average-closing-time-info":"This company presented an average time of {positionsClosingTime} days to close its job postings in the last three months.","position-average-closing-time":"Average time for closing a job posting of {positionsClosingTime} days","hired-celebration-congratulations":"","hired-celebration-message-1":"You have achieved a new milestone! We know how much you dedicated yourself, and now you can celebrate your approval in all stages of this position!","hired-celebration-message-2":"Attention! Regularly check your <b>email</b> (including the spam folder) and the <b>phone</b> you registered. The next steps are on the way, and every detail matters!","hired-celebration-message-3":"We are excited to celebrate this achievement together!","hired-celebration-message-4":"How about celebrating with your network that you made it to the final stage? Share this victory!","hired-celebration-message-5":"Copy the text below and share it on your LinkedIn!","hired-celebration-share-on-linkedin":"Share on LinkedIn","hired-celebration-share":"Share","hired-celebration-share-message-desktop":"","hired-celebration-share-message-mobile":"I am very pleased to share that I have reached the final stage of the {jobName} position at {companyName} through the Gupy platform!","hired-celebration-close":"Not now, thank you","hired-celebration-copy":"Copy","rate-gupy-process":"","talent-pool-job-application-message":"You have applied to the talent pool of {companyName}!","talent-pool-job-other-opportunities":"Now, how about exploring other opportunities?","access-career-page-button":"Access Career Page","access-portal-button":"Access Job Portal","step_card_unavailable_test_tip_title":"","step_card_unavailable_test_tip_description":"","viewed_curriculum":"<strong>Your resume has been viewed</strong> by the recruiting person","expired_at_deadline":"Expired on: {deadline}","expires_at_deadline":"Deadline: {deadline}","expires_at_time_limit":"Maximum duration: {timeLimit}","step_card_reuse_tip_start":"","step_card_reuse_tip":"Test Reuse: You have performed this test before. To reuse your score or take the test again, click \\"Start\\".","skipped_video":"Step skipped.","skipped_test":"Step skipped.","video_uploaded":"Don\u2019t worry, your video has been sent to the company!","external_test_link_missing_title":"Failed to start test","external_test_link_missing_message":"Unfortunately we could not start your test right now. To continue, try refreshing your page. \\n\\n\xA0If the problem persists, try again later.","refresh_page":"Update page","generating_test":"Generating test","start_test":"Begin assessment","application_dashboard_hero_footer_step_offline_completed":"Step finished.","start":"Start","profile_test_introduction_button_next":"Start","profile_test_topic2_button_next":"Start","view":"See","fill_data":"Fill in data","unlock_previous_steps_first":"You must complete the previous steps to be able to move forward in the process.","wait_answer_company":"You haven\u2019t reached this step yet! But don\u2019t worry, we\u2019re reviewing the previous steps and will let you know as soon as we have an update.","step_final_card_title":"Final Step","application-dashboard-register-curriculum":"Resume","resume":"Resume","application-dashboard-register-profile":"Profile assessment","profile-text__title":"Profile assessment","pre_hire_step_message":"Fill in and send your information so that it is possible to proceed with the selection process","loading":"Loading","curriculum_skills_ariaLabelLoader":"Loading","guided-application-loading-aria-label":"Loading","viewed":"Viewed","answer":"Reply","curriculum_messages_reply":"Reply","technologist-degree-tip":"MEC