ional company questions to complete the application step. But if you want, you can review your data.","personalization_dialog_title":"Introduce yourself!","guided-application-personalization-title":"Introduce yourself!","personalization_dialog_finish_application":"Finish application","guided-application-finish-applcation":"Finish application","personalization_dialog_start_personalization":"Personalize application","personalization_dialog_optional":"Optional","personalization_dialog_text_top":"Now you can make a personal introduction and highlight your main skills to make your application more attractive to the company.","personalization_dialog_text_mid":"The customization is valid exclusively for this position.","personalization_dialog_text_bottom":"This process is quick and takes an average of 3 minutes!","birth-date-title":"Date of birth","birthdate":"Date of birth","birthDate":"Date of birth","containers/user-profile/birthdate-label":"Date of birth","birth-date-dialog-placeholder":"mm/dd/yyyy","birthdate_placeholder":"mm/dd/yyyy","containers/user-profile/birthdate-placeholder":"mm/dd/yyyy","birth-date-dialog-content":"It seems you haven't filled in your date of birth in your profile, and in order for you to participate in the platform's selection processes, we need this information.","birth-date-dialog-fill":"Please fill in the field below and proceed with your application.","birth-date-dialog-give-up":"Withdraw","give_up":"Withdraw","birth-date-dialog-save":"Save and continue","save_and_continue":"Save and continue","guided_application_save_and_continue":"Save and continue","save_answer_and_go_to_next_question":"Save and continue","birth-date-dialog-infotip":"It is necessary to be at least 14 years old to participate in the selection processes","birth-date-dialog-minimum-age-error":"You must be at least 14 years old to participate in the selection processes, but we can wait until you are ready.","containers/user-profile/minimum-age":"You must be at least 14 years old to participate in the selection processes, but we can wait until you are ready.","birth-date-dialog-invalid-age-error":"Invalid date","invalid_date":"Invalid date","invalid-date":"Invalid date","containers/user-profile/invalid-date":"Invalid date","birth-date-dialog-maximum-age-error":"Invalid year","candidate-empty-skills":"<b>You haven't added any skills to your resume yet. </b> Add skills so you can highlight them here.","candidate_highlighted_skill_counter":"<b>{length}</b> / 3 selected skills","personalization-step-title":"The company wants to know more about you!","personalization-step-subtitle":"Tell us about yourself and your professional journey, explaining how you can help the company with the challenge described in the job posting.","personalization-step-placeholder":"Write here\u2026","personalization-step-skills-title":"What are your most valuable skills for this position?","personalization-step-skills-subtitle":"Choose up to 3 skills from those registered in your resume that you would like to highlight for the recruiter.","personalization_step_highlighted_skills":"Highlighted skills","personalization-step-img-alt":"Young man looking upwards with MANIFESTO in the background and the phrase DA EXPERI\xCANCIA DA PESSOA CANDIDATA","personalization-step-text-count":"<b>{length}</b> / 1.500 characters","personalization-step-tip":"Personalization in the application is part of the commitments of the <b>Candidate Experience Manifesto<b/>","skills_help_center_subtitle":"You can list up to 30 skills you possess. (Skills can range from technical knowledge to the way you relate to people). For more information, visit our <a href=\u201Chttps://suporte-candidatos.gupy.io/s/suporte?language=pt_BR\u201D target=\\"_blank\\">Help center.</a>","curriculum-skills-count":"{itemsLength} out of 30 skills","curriculum_skills_title":"Skills","curriculum_click_to_remove_skill":"","curriculum_skills_search_label":"Skill (optional)","curriculum_skills_search_placeholder":"Write and select a skill","curriculum_skills_search_help_button":"Didn't find the skill you're looking for? Leave a comment.","curriculum_skills_add":"Add","application_step_video_reused_add_video":"Add","/curriculum/components/footer/add":"Add","curriculum_skills_suggest":"","curriculum_skills_send":"Send","to-send":"Send","messages_button_send":"Send","curriculum_skills_to_delete":"Skills to be excluded","curriculum_click_to_add_skill_again":"","curriculum_click_warn":"Don't forget to click the \\"Save\\" button after making changes.","curriculum_skills_limit_reached":"Limit reached","curriculum_skills_limit_reached_dialog_text":"You have reached the limit of 30 registered skills. If you want to add a new one, please delete an existing one.","skill_suggestions_dialog_title":"Leave a comment","skill_suggestions_dialog_text":"Let us know which skill(s) you felt were missing from the list:","skill_suggestions_input_label":"Skill (limit of 10 suggestions)","skill_suggestions_toast":"We've received your comment, and our team will evaluate your suggestion","skill_suggestions_error":"","skill_synonyms_subtitle":"","has_highlighted_skills":"One or more skills were highlighted in the \\"Introduce Yourself\\" stage of your applications. If you remove them from your resume, they will also be removed as highlights in the applications.","saving":"Saving","something_went_wrong_try_again_later":"","fill_out_previous_steps_to_unlock_steps_below":"To release the following steps, complete the information above and click the button <strong>Save and continue</strong>.","problem_loading_curriculum_data":"We had a problem loading the information","try_again":"Try again","confirm_sending_answers":"<strong>Do you wish to confirm the submission of your answers?</strong><br>These are the requirements defined as disqualifying by {currentCompanyName}.","curriculum-container-job-name":"Resume - {jobName}","month-date-placeholder":"Month","year-date-placeholder":"Year","month-jan":"January","month-fev":"February","month-mar":"March","month-abr":"April","month-mai":"May","month-jun":"June","month-jul":"July","month-ago":"August","month-set":"September","month-out":"October","month-nov":"November","month-dez":"December","invalid_email_error":"The email <strong>{email}</strong>, used to identify who has referred you to the job does not exist or is incorrect. Some companies may choose to accept only corporate email addresses. To proceed, you need to <strong>fix the corporate email address</strong> of the person who has referred you or deselect the option whether or not you were referred to this position.","info_curriculo_upload_modal_item_one":"<strong>DOCX</strong> format tend to have a higher filling efficiency.","info_curriculo_upload_modal_item_two":"A <strong>simple formatted 1-column</strong> CV <strong>with no images</strong> is better availed by technology.","info_curriculo_upload_modal_item_four":"The CV sent <strong>will not be evaluated by the company</strong>. It will only be used to<strong> fill the CV here at Gupy</strong>.","info_curriculo_upload_modal_title":"Tips to use your CV","info_curriculo_upload_modal_message_title":"Avoid autofill problems!","info_curriculo_upload_modal_message_button_ok":"Ok, I got it!","curriculum_parse_modal_title":"You have already filled in the information on your resume","curriculum-upload-prevent-override-title":"You have already filled in the information on your resume","curriculum_parse_modal_text":"When submitting a resume for autofill, <b>you will overwrite information already filled in.</b> Do you want to continue anyway?","curriculum-upload-prevent-override-description":"When submitting a resume for autofill, <b>you will overwrite information already filled in.</b> Do you want to continue anyway?","curriculum_parse_modal_aprove":"Replace with a prepared resume","curriculum-upload-prevent-override-confirm-button":"Replace with a prepared resume","curriculum_parse_modal_back":"Do not replace","curriculum-upload-prevent-override-close-button":"Do not replace","curriculum_experiment_linkedin_pdf_message":"","curriculum_upload_title":"Want to save time using your resume? (Optional)","curriculum_upload_description":"You can upload your CV in PDF or DOCX format and <strong>use to autofill</strong> your informations.","curriculum_upload_tip":"See the tips","analyzing_data":"Analyzing information","curriculum-upload-loading":"Analyzing information","find_file":"Search file","see_hint":"See hint","only_doc_docx_pdf_html_rtf_or_open_office_will_be_accepted":"Only DOC, DOCX, PDF, HTML, RTF or Open Office files are accepted","try_again_or_skip_this_step":"Try uploading your file again or fill it out manually. Remember, only files in DOCX and PDF formats are accepted. Note: the PDF cannot be in image format.","curriculum_upload_success":"File was uploaded successfully!","my_curriculum_subtitle":"Fill in the fields with your information and keep your resume up to date to apply for job openings. If you make changes, these adjustments will be <b>replicated for all your active applications.</b>","your_experience_card":"Experience","diversity":"Diversity","info_modal_title":"Diversity","diversity_hint_tip":"Completing this section is optional. The information will be used in all processes that utilize the Diversity solution. No data will be used as an elimination criterion.","info_modal_tip_content_p3":"The objective is to contribute to fairer and more diverse evaluations, where candidate individuals do not suffer discrimination based on their gender, gender identity, color or race, sexual orientation, and place of birth.","info_modal_tip_content_p1":"Your information will be made available for analysis and actions focused on diversity.","info_modal_tip_content_p2":"It is important to remember: your data will never be used as elimination criteria in selection processes.","info_modal_identity_content_p1":"Gender is understood by society as something binary and immutable. But in reality, there is a spectrum of identities that need not coincide with biological gender.","info_modal_identity_content_p2":"However, a person who socially positions himself as a transsexual has reduced chances of being employed.","info_modal_identity_content_p3":"The goal is to change this reality with data and contribute to affirmative actions in Recruitment & Selection strategies.","info_modal_sexual_orientation_content_p2":"The goal is to change this reality with data and contribute to affirmative actions in Recruitment & Selection strategies.","info_modal_origin_fields_content_p3":"The goal is to change this reality with data and contribute to affirmative actions in Recruitment & Selection strategies.","info_modal_identity_content_p4":"It is important to remember: your data will never be used as elimination criteria in selection processes. With them, companies are able to conduct diversity analyses and reduce biases in the processes.","info_modal_origin_fields_content_p4":"It is important to remember: your data will never be used as elimination criteria in selection processes. With them, companies are able to conduct diversity analyses and reduce biases in the processes.","info_modal_sexual_orientation_content_p1":"Sexual orientation still affects a person's perception of merit and ability. Furthermore, conservatism can get mixed up with organizational decisions and this directly restricts hiring non-heterosexual people.","info_modal_sexual_orientation_content_p3":"It is important to remember: your data will never be used as elimination criteria in selection processes. With them, companies are able to conduct diversity analyses and reduce biases in the processes.","info_modal_race_color_content_p1":"A person's color or race influences many aspects of their life. In Brazil, structural racism affects income, access to goods and services, career opportunities and much more.","info_modal_race_color_content_p2":"In the labor market, this results in very unequal distributions of people of different colors or races, making the employability of some groups higher than others - which is even more discrepant in high positions.","info_modal_race_color_content_p3":"The goal is to change this reality with data and contribute to affirmative actions in Recruitment & Selection strategies.","info_modal_race_color_content_p4":"It is important to remember: your data will never be used as elimination criteria in selection processes. With them, companies are able to conduct diversity analyses and reduce biases in the processes.","checkbox-consent-diversity-info-label-with-company":"I agree to share this data with {currentCompanyName} and other companies in order to carry out actions aimed at promoting diversity.","checkbox-consent-diversity-info-label-without-company":"I agree to share this data with companies in order to carry out actions aimed at promoting diversity","info_modal_origin_fields_content_p1":"A person's place of birth, in addition to relating to their culture and customs, affects access to jobs.","info_modal_origin_fields_content_p2":"Today, in Brazil, there are still job hub cities, causing individuals from other cities to invest much more effort to obtain career opportunities. Nevertheless, these individuals still face the risk of experiencing prejudice based on their place of origin.","info_modal_tip_button_text":"Why fill in this information?","gender_pronoun_field_title":"Which pronoun is right for you:","gender_pronoun_him_field":"He / Him","gender_pronoun_her_field":"She / Her","info_modal_identity_title":"Gender identity","gender_identity_field_title":"What is your gender identity:","gender_identity_cis_field":"Cisgender","gender_identity_trans_field":"Transgender","info_modal_identity_button_text":"What's the importance of gender identity ?","info_modal_identity_content_title":"What is the importance of filling out your gender identity?","info_modal_orientation_title":"Sexual orientation","sexual_orientation_field_title":"What is your sexual orientation:","sexual_orientation_heterosexual_field":"Heterosexual","sexual_orientation_homosexual_field":"Homosexual","sexual_orientation_bisexual_field":"Bisexual","sexual_orientation_asexual_field":"Assexual","sexual_orientation_pansexual_field":"Pansexual","info_modal_sexual_orientation_button_text":"What's the importance of sexual orientation ?","info_modal_sexual_orientation_content_title":"What's the importance of filling in your sexual orientation ?","tip_heterosexual":"Heterosexual: is the person who is attracted to people of the gender considered opposite to this person's gender.","tip_homosexual":"Homosexual: is the person who is attracted to people of the same gender.","tip_bisexual":"Bisexual: is the person who is attracted to two or more genders.","tip_asexual":"Asexual: person who experiences little or no sexual attraction.","tip_pansexual":"Pansexual: is the person who is attracted to people of all genders.","tip_pronoun":"Pronoun: the pronoun is related to the gender identity of each person, that is, the way in which they identify and want to be called social","info_modal_race_color_title":"Race or skin color","race_color_field_title":"What\u2019s your race or skin color:","race_color_white_field":"White","race_color_black_field":"Black","race_color_pardo_field":"Brown","race_color_indigenous_field":"Indigenous","race_color_yellow_field":"Asian","info_modal_race_color_button_text":"What's the importance of race/color?","info_modal_race_color_content_title":"What's the importance of filling in your race/color ?","no_anwser_field":"I prefer not to disclose","gender_no_answer":"I prefer not to disclose","tip_cisgender":"Cisgender: (or cis) is a term for people whose gender identity matches their gender assigned at birth.","tip_transgender":"Transgender: (or trans) is a term for people whose gender identity is different from their gender assigned at birth.","info_modal_tip_content_title":"Why fill in diversity information ?","info_modal_origin_title":"Place of birth","state_of_origin_field_title":"State of origin:","city_of_origin_field_title":"City of origin:","origin_fields_button_text":"What\u2019s the importance of filling in your place of birth ?","info_modal_origin_fields_content_title":"What\u2019s the importance of filling in your place of birth ?","cities_options_empty":"First, choose a state of origin","consent_diversity_info_share":"Consent to information sharing","checkbox_consent_diversity_info_label_link":"Access Gupy's","checkbox_consent_diversity_info_label_link_page":"Privacy Notice.","company_questions_title":"Questions created by the company {currentCompanyName}","confirm_application_title":"Hello {name}, shall we continue with your application?","confirm_application_description":"You are applying for the <b>{job} position at {company}.<b/>","confirm_company_questions_title":"Company created questions","additional_questions_block_title_with_company":"Company created questions","confirm_company_questions_description":"<b>{name}, this position has question(s) created by {company}.</b> To continue with the process, please answer the following questions.","confirm_company_questions_description_no_edit":"<b>Attention:</b> the answers cannot be edited later.","guided-application-curriculum-description":"Fill in the sections with your information and keep your resume updated to apply for job openings.\\n            If you make any changes, these adjustments will be  <b>replicated across all your active applications.</b>","curriculum-upload-description":"You can upload your ready-made resume and <b>try to leverage information</b> with our auto-fill feature. (optional)","curriculum-upload-add-file":"Add file","curriculum-upload-accepted-files":"The resume file must be in the formats: DOCX or PDF.","curriculum-upload-error":"Try uploading your file again or fill it in manually. Remember, only files in DOCX and PDF formats are accepted. Note: the PDF cannot be in image format.","curriculum-upload-success":"File uploaded successfully. Review the data and correct any errors if necessary.","fill_out_curriculum_title":"Hello {name}","fill_out_curriculum_description":"To continue with your application, you need to <b>complete your Resume.</b>","guided-application-finish-text-top":"The company <b>{companyName}</b> will now analyze your compatibility with the position and decide if you advance to the next stages.","guided-application-finish-text-bottom":"<b>Keep an eye on your email</b> (including the spam folder) and the <b>phone number you registered</b> to stay informed of the next steps","guided-application-finish-opt-in":"Your r\xE9sum\xE9 is now available in the Gupy Talent Pool, allowing interested companies to invite you to new selection processes. Your diversity data will only be shared if you allow it. To adjust this setting, go to your <a href='https://login.gupy.io/candidates/profile/manage-talent-portal/' target='_blank'>sharing preferences<a/>.","preview-curriculum-empty-section":"<b>No descriptions in this section.</b> Add your data to stand out!","professional-experience-current-period":"(from {startMonth}/{startYear} - currently)","professional-experience-period":"(from {startMonth}/{startYear} to {endMonth}/{endYear})","professional-experience-empty-activities-text":"<b>No information in this section.</b> Add your data to stand out!","guided-application-continue":"Continue","continue":"Continue","passwordless_signin_continue_btn":"Continue","sign_up_continue":"Continue","forgot_password_submit_button":"Send link","profile_test_topic1_button_next":"Continue","guided_application_additional_data_title":"Additional information","guided_application_additional_data_where_you_find_this_vacancy_description":"Where did you find this job? (Optional)","guided_application_additional_data_how_did_you_hear_about_us":"Choose an option","guided_application_additional_data_corporate_email_title":"Provide your corporate email","guided_application_additional_data_corporate_email_empty_error_message":"Please fill in your corporate email","guided_application_additional_data_corporate_email_invalid_error_message":"It seems that this email is not valid. Please check it","guided_application_additional_data_is_indicated_title":"Someone who works at this company referred you for this position?","guided_application_additional_data_indicated_by_name":"Name of the person who recommended you","guided_application_additional_data_indicated_by_name_placeholder":"Enter the name of your manager or direct leader","guided_application_additional_data_indicated_by_name_empty_error_message":"Fill in the name of the person who recommended you","guided_application_additional_data_indicated_by_email":"E-mail of the person who has referred you","guided_application_additional_data_indicated_by_email_placeholder":"Enter the email of your manager or direct leader","guided_application_additional_data_indicated_by_email_invalid_error_message":"This email does not appear to be corporate. Correct it or uncheck the option if you were not recommended for this position.","guided_application_additional_data_know_more":"See more","manage_privacy_setting_know_more":"See more","talent_portal_link_see_more":"See more","guided-application-reply-now":"Answer now","guided-application-eliminatory-questions":"(eliminatory questions)","guided-application-personalization-subtitle":"(optional stage)","guided-application-finish-application-title":"Application Completed!","guided-application-track-application":"Track application","guided-application-review-curriculum":"Review my curriculum","guided-application-expired-step":"Stage expired","guided-application-expired-step-description":"Unfortunately, you can no longer complete this stage of the selection process.","guided-application-expired-step-description-bottom":"The period to complete this stage ended on","guided-application-fill-out-curriculum":"Complete resume","curriculum_register_new_curriculum_action":"Complete resume","guided-application-fill-out-curriculum-description":"Don\u2019t worry, we will hold this position and at the end of the completion, you will be able to continue your application!","guided-application-continue-application":"Continue Application","preview-curriculum-close-btn":"Close resume preview","preview-curriculum-edit-btn":"Edit Resume","preview-curriculum-professional-experiences":"Professional experience","professional_experience_section_title":"Professional experience","professional_experience":"Professional experience","preview-curriculum-show-more":"Show more","preview-curriculum-show-less":"Show less","preview-curriculum-she-her-pronoun":"She/Her","preview-curriculum-he-him-pronoun":"He/His","basic":"Basic","intermediate":"Intermediate","advanced":"Advanced","fluent":"Native/Fluent","german":"German","arabic":"Arabic","bengali":"Bengali","kazakh":"Kazakh","chinese":"Chinese","korean":"Korean","haitian_creole":"Haitian Creole","kurdish":"Kurdish","spanish":"Spanish","french":"French","greek":"Greek","hindi":"Hindi","hungarian":"Hungarian","italian":"Italian","japanese":"Japanese","javanese":"Javanese","lahnda":"Lahnda","malay":"Malay","dutch":"Dutch","nepali":"Nepali","persian":"Persian","polish":"Polish","portuguese":"Portuguese","portugues":"Portuguese","romanian":"Romanian","russian":"Russian","serbo_croatian":"Serbo-Croatian","somali":"Somali","swedish":"Swedish","thai":"Thai","czech":"Czech","turkish":"Turkish","ukrainian":"Ukrainian","vietnamese":"Vietnamese","languages_section_title":"Language","language":"Language","languages_section_first_subtitle":"You can talk about a course, voluntary work or other recognitions","languages_section_subtitle":"Select all the languages you speak.","add_language":"Add another language","add_first_language":"Add a language","remove_language":"Remove language","select_an_language":"Select a language","language_level":"Level","level":"Level","select_a_level":"Select the level","empty_level":"Fill the level","field_required_error":"This field is required","maximum_value_error":"The maximum value has been exceeded:","minimum_value_error":"The minimum value has been exceeded:","valid_value_choice_error":"Choose one of the valid values","invalid_field_type":"Invalid field type","eliminatory_question":"disqualifying","additional_information":"Additional information","job_details_relevant_experiencies":"Additional information","qualifying_step":"disqualifying step","additional_info_block_title":"Application information","additional_questions_block_title_experiment":"Job Questions","eliminatory_questions_review":" Review of disqualifying questions","answers":"Answers","review":"Review","confirm":"Confirm","confirm_button_text":"Confirm","receiving_resume":"Receiving resume","receiving_additional_questions":"Receiving additional questions","analysing_requirements_vacancy":" Analyzing the requirements of the vacancy","finishing":"Finishing","description_resume_submission":"Saving your resume information","eliminatory_company_questions_tip":"The questions may be eliminatory according to the criteria established by the company and cannot be edited.","default_company_questions_tip":"Answers cannot be edited later.","my_address_is_not_in_list_add_manually":"My address is not on the list, I will add it manually...","your_address":"Your address","type_address_sample":"Example: Av. Santa Monica, 56, Rio de Janeiro, Brasil","commute_availability_title":"Displacement availability (optional)","commute_availability_description":"Remember, this information will be used in <strong>all</strong> your applications.","commute_availability_checkbox_title":"Select your displacement availability:","commute_availability_country_travel":"I accept to work in another country","commute_availability_state_travel":"I accept to work in another state","commute_availability_city_travel":"I accept to work in other cities","commute_availability_remote":"I accept to work remotely (Home Office)","disability_required_link_privacy_policy":"Would you like to apply to this job as a person with disabilities? Learn more about our <a href=\\"https://login.gupy.io/candidates/gupy-privacy\\" target=\\"_blank\\">privacy notice.</a>","linkedin_title":"<strong>LinkedIn Profile</strong>","disability_document_deletion_success":"The file {fileName} was successfully deleted!","disability_document_save_success":"The file {fileName} was successfully included!","about_you":"About you","curriculum/pages/profile/components/profile-details/title":"About you","gender_field":"Gender","gender_field_description":"Select the gender you identify with","gender_female":"Female","gender_male":"Male","gender_non_binary":"Non-binary","gender_others":"Others","disability_field":"Disability","disability_type":"Specify Disability","disability_cid":"Corresponding CID","empty_disability_type_error":"Select an option to add another disability","duplicated_disability_error":"Duplicated disability type and CID","disability_input_cid":"Type CID","disability_form_hint":"Filling in the disability fields is optional, but it can help ensure accessibility and inclusion in the selection process.","disability_add_item":"Add one more Disability","disability_upload_report_title":"Send the Medical Report to complement your application","disability_text_upload_report":"The Medical Report is important to ensure that the selection processes for people with a disability are fair and that only people with a disability participate in them. In this way, recruiting companies will be able to quickly identify inappropriate applications, making the selection process more agile and fair.\\n\\nAs the submission of the medical report is not mandatory, you will not be automatically disqualified from the selection process. However, this control will be exclusive to the contracting companies, which may use this document to avoid fraud.\\n\\nThe report will be collected and stored based on your consent, therefore, if you wish, you can delete this attachment at any time from your profile. This document will be shared only with the companies that hire the vacancies in which you applied and with those that need to receive it to enable their participation in the selection process, according to our privacy notice.","disability_reports_file_formats":"This document can be in the formats: PNG, JPG, JPEG, DOC, DOCX or PDF.","disability_modal_confirmation_title":"Do you want to delete the file?","disability_modal_confirmation_message":"The file attached as PCD Report will be deleted, you can attach it again if necessary.","disability_cancel":"Cancel","cancel":"Cancel","application_step_video_send_video_cancel_button":"Cancel","/curriculum/components/footer/cancel":"Cancel","disability_loading":"Loading...","disability_include_file":"Include File","disability_file_extension_error":"Unsupported file format. Check if the file has one of these characteristics:","disability_physical_disability":"Physical disability","disability_visual_impairment":"Visual disability","disability_hearing_deficiency":"Hearing disability","disability_mental_disability":"Mental disability","disability_intellectual_deficiency":"Intellectual disability","disability_autism_spectrum_disorder":"Autistic Spectrum Disorderss","disability_remove_item":"Remove disability","linkedin_description":"Your profile URL link (optional)","curriculum/pages/profile/components/social-form/label":"Your profile URL link (optional)","linkedin_placeholder":"Ex: www.linkedin.com/in/id","you_have_more_than_maximum_age":"Please select a year higher than {year}.","containers/user-profile/maximum-age":"Please select a year higher than {year}.","you_do_not_have_minimum_age":"It looks like you are not old enough to be able to sign up. But I can wait until you\u2019re ready.","address_min_len_zip_code":"Enter a valid 8-digit zip code","empty_address_country":"Fill in the country","empty_address_state":"Fill in the state","empty_address_city":"Fill in the city","empty_address_street":"Fill in the address","empty_address_zip_code":"Fill in the zip code","cid_without_disability_type":"To register the CID, the type of disability must be entered.","tip_description_activities_error":"<strong>Avoid:</strong> \u201CI proactively worked on a project that involved doing complex index calculations, exposing slide presentation skills\u2026\u201D","tip_description_activities_success":"\u201CExperience with projects, calculation of indexes, presentations, creation of slides\u201D","tip_description_activities":"This information is very important to analyze and classify your resume according to the job requirements.","professional_experience_section_subtitle":"You can add more than one professional experience, if necessary.","company":"Company","role":"Position","add_first_professional_experience":"Add one professional experience","add_professional_experience":"Add another professional experience","remove_professional_experience":"Remove experience","my_current_job":"This is my current job","activities_description":"Main activities carried out","activities_description_placeholder":"List objectively the activities developed in this experience","activities_description_cta":"To see tips, click here.","activities_description_modal_title":"Tips for your CV","activities_description_modal_description":"Two quick tips to boost the quality of your resume writing, check them out:","activities_description_modal_first_item":"Be careful when writing your resume: write with examples, results, lessons learned, tools used, etc;","activities_description_modal_second_item":"Highlight your experience: provide relevant details, describe your responsibilities and the activities you took part in;","activities_description_modal_third_item":"Register your CV according to the language of the vacancy;","activities_description_modal_fourth_item":"Avoid writing long texts and telling stories. Write 3 to 4 one-line topics.","activities_description_modal_complement":"If you\u2019d like to learn more about how to fill out a resume","activities_description_modal_complement_link":"Visit Gupy's YouTube channel.","activities_description_modal_example":"Example:","empty_company_name":"Fill in the company name","empty_role":"Fill the position","pre-hire-job-name":"Pre-hire - {name}","pre-hire-submit-button":"Submit data","question-form":"","answer-the-strategic-questions":"","when-you-click-save":"","fill-in-carefully":"","the-information-is-requested-directly-by-the-company":"","submit-question-form-responses":"","select-one-or-more-options":"","no-options":"","enter-your-answer-here":"","required":"","privacy-notice":"Privacy notice","new_signup_experience_privacy_policy":"Privacy notice","talent_portal_link_privacy_notice":"Privacy notice","test_result":"Assessment result","test_result_title":"Behavioral Mapping stage","test_result_view_score":"You can view your results by clicking \\"View results\\"","test_result_back_info":"And to return to your application, click \\"Back to home page\\".","test_result_back_url":"Back to home page","test_result_more_info":"If you\u2019d like to learn more about Gupy\u2019s psychometric assessments,","test_result_more_info_contact":"feel free to contact","test_result_more_info_end":"us.","test_result_score_result":"Your result was","your_result":"Your result was","reuse_completion_result_info":"Your result was","test_result_score_of_total":"of 100","test_result_english_test_title":"English Assessment","test_result_portuguese_test_title":"Portuguese Assessment","test_result_numerical_reasoning_complete_test_title":"Complete Logical and Numerical Reasoning Test","test_result_numerical_reasoning_essential_test_title":"Essential Logical and Numerical Reasoning Test","test_result_verbal_reasoning_complete_test_title":"Complete Verbal Reasoning Test","test_result_verbal_reasoning_essential_test_title":"Essential Verbal Reasoning Test","test_result_sales_situational_test_title":"Sales Situational Technical Test",